		<!-- message -->
		<div>Howdy.  I've got a 68 druid, 65 chanter, and 62 warrior.  I've got a CRT, a laptop, and two LCD's on my desk, and I'm trying to figure out a good way to grow into one more LCD so I can 4-box.<br />
<br />
I'm just wondering, who out there 3-4 boxes (or more) and what desk, keyboard(s), and mice do you use to control all of them at once?<br />
<br />
Reply to this post or PM me, I'm considering getting a new desk if there's one that will fit my needs better than my current one.<br />
<br />
Thanks in advance.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
